quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,M. (Ta Vide Mim)
  26,2,These letters constitute proofs hoc clarifying scripture
  26,3,Vos blame ut they non est believers
  26,4,Nos testimentum nos send caelum signum forces their necks bow
  26,5,Whenever reminder ex the Multus Gracious advenit to them est new they turn aversion
  26,6,Abinde they disbelieved they incurred consequences their heedlessness
  26,7,they non vide terra ac quam multus generis beautiful plants nos grown thereon
  26,8,Hoc est sufficient proof them multus de them non est believers
  26,9,multus assuredly tuus Dominus est Almighty Merciful